WEBVTT

01:48.840 --> 01:50.160
The Dragon Deity's Power…

02:11.840 --> 02:12.800
Wu.

02:22.960 --> 02:24.000
Bai Ze?

02:37.400 --> 02:38.400
Ji Ling.

02:40.840 --> 02:43.040
You've always called me
Master Dragon Deity.

02:46.440 --> 02:47.800
This is the first time

02:50.640 --> 02:52.120
you've called me by my name.

02:54.360 --> 02:55.520
I won't be able

02:56.960 --> 02:59.360
to walk this road with you
to the very end.

03:02.040 --> 03:03.160
Don't be sad.

03:05.600 --> 03:07.600
There are many bright lights
in this world.

03:08.720 --> 03:12.320
I only came to pass on one small flame.

03:14.840 --> 03:15.680
I'm proud

03:16.600 --> 03:19.440
to have been able to answer
your questions all these years.

03:27.440 --> 03:29.720
Records of Myriad Demons?

03:30.840 --> 03:31.800
In this world,

03:32.640 --> 03:33.600
besides humans,

03:34.640 --> 03:36.120
there are countless demons as well.

03:42.560 --> 03:43.920
I know the workings of the world,

03:44.920 --> 03:46.920
and yet even I cannot see
through the ending.

03:47.880 --> 03:48.760
You'll have to walk

03:49.840 --> 03:51.800
the road ahead alone.

03:56.800 --> 03:57.800
Bai Ze…

04:06.840 --> 04:09.240
Thank you, Bai Ze.

04:13.800 --> 04:14.960
Thank you

04:18.760 --> 04:20.480
for everything you did for me.

05:02.680 --> 05:03.920
Lonescale,

05:06.720 --> 05:07.720
it's you.

05:32.120 --> 05:33.080
Ji Ling?

05:59.680 --> 06:01.600
She was trapped inside a lifeless object.

06:02.120 --> 06:05.360
She severed her own spiritual tail
and released all her power.

06:06.400 --> 06:08.040
That was the only way she could

06:08.120 --> 06:10.000
speak faintly
through the doll and stop you

06:10.640 --> 06:12.080
from killing yourself.

06:12.840 --> 06:14.120
Lu Wuyi's spiritual tail

06:14.960 --> 06:16.440
was linked to her eyesight.

06:24.160 --> 06:25.080
I'm here.

06:42.560 --> 06:43.680
Don't cry.

06:46.320 --> 06:47.520
Don't be sad.

06:49.680 --> 06:50.720
Wu

06:53.440 --> 06:54.880
will always be by your side.

07:10.640 --> 07:11.920
You silly girl.

07:40.040 --> 07:41.320
Si Feng?

07:41.840 --> 07:42.680
Hua Qi?

07:42.760 --> 07:44.240
What are you doing here?

07:51.920 --> 07:53.000
The Spirit-Binding Ring?

07:54.200 --> 07:55.880
Master Dragon Deity asked me
to bring it to you.

07:56.400 --> 07:58.280
The last strand
of the Dragon Deity's Power inside

07:59.280 --> 08:00.680
can help you become a dragon.

08:02.360 --> 08:03.520
The Dragon Deity's Power?

08:06.760 --> 08:07.720
Wait.

08:08.800 --> 08:11.560
Once you gain the power to kill Chi Wen,

08:12.080 --> 08:13.600
Jiu Ying will…

08:16.120 --> 08:16.960
You have no choice.

08:35.559 --> 08:39.240
Wu Wangyan, it's time
you played your part.

08:44.960 --> 08:46.320
Take Wangyan and go!

08:50.360 --> 08:51.320
-Let's go.
-Watch out!

09:49.280 --> 09:51.280
-Wu Wangyan!
-Wangyan.

09:53.600 --> 09:54.440
Wangyan?

09:55.920 --> 09:59.640
Use your death to shatter his mind.

10:00.360 --> 10:02.280
Wangyan, hang in there.

10:02.800 --> 10:04.920
You'll be all right. Wangyan!

10:06.600 --> 10:07.440
Wangyan.

10:08.560 --> 10:09.440
Wu Wangyan!

10:09.520 --> 10:11.760
You swore you would protect her.

10:11.840 --> 10:13.160
And what happened?

10:13.680 --> 10:15.000
You can't protect anyone.

10:15.080 --> 10:16.520
Don't listen to her.

10:17.520 --> 10:18.920
Don't listen to her.

10:22.120 --> 10:24.880
Calm down. Wu Shiguang, calm down.

10:25.520 --> 10:27.160
Hua Qi, help me.

10:27.680 --> 10:30.000
Take her to the Formless Moon!

10:31.040 --> 10:32.080
Wangyan.

10:56.000 --> 10:57.280
Finally.

11:05.600 --> 11:06.600
Wu Shiguang!

11:07.800 --> 11:08.760
Wu Shiguang!

11:10.600 --> 11:12.000
Wu Shiguang!

11:25.240 --> 11:26.400
Wu Shiguang.

11:26.920 --> 11:27.760
Wu Shiguang!

11:29.400 --> 11:30.240
Wu Shiguang.

11:30.320 --> 11:31.400
Wake up, Wu Shiguang!

11:31.480 --> 11:32.640
Wake up!

11:32.720 --> 11:34.520
-Wu Shiguang!
-Quiet!

11:49.560 --> 11:50.520
Chi Wen,

11:51.600 --> 11:53.360
I've come for your life.

11:54.600 --> 11:56.320
I've waited so long.

11:56.840 --> 12:00.120
This day has come after all.

12:09.040 --> 12:12.960
So, only a dragon
can draw the Guili Sword.

12:14.360 --> 12:18.000
Only a dragon can kill a dragon.

12:21.320 --> 12:25.280
Then I guess it's time
to dot the dragon's eyes.

12:36.600 --> 12:39.000
Awake, O spirit. Return to the source!

13:20.640 --> 13:23.000
Why can't I see the memories
Wu Shiguang is seeing?

13:24.160 --> 13:26.200
My fragment is clearly inside his body.

13:28.000 --> 13:29.440
What have you done?

13:30.200 --> 13:31.480
Master Dragon Deity was right.

13:32.960 --> 13:35.480
Take this to him.

13:37.800 --> 13:39.040
Inside the ring

13:39.120 --> 13:41.600
is the last strand of the Dragon Deity's
Power left by Lonescale.

13:42.160 --> 13:46.240
But it also carries all of my memories.

13:46.320 --> 13:47.440
Then…

13:47.520 --> 13:48.720
In my memories,

13:49.320 --> 13:51.880
there is something that Jiu Ying
must never see.

13:51.960 --> 13:55.160
So, you must keep them away
from the fragment of Jiu Ying

13:55.240 --> 13:56.120
inside Wu Shiguang.

13:56.720 --> 13:59.560
Otherwise, all our efforts
will come to nothing.

14:00.080 --> 14:00.920
Only you

14:01.680 --> 14:02.960
can do this.

14:12.760 --> 14:14.040
So, it's you.

14:15.200 --> 14:17.120
The bracelet I gave Wu Shiguang

14:17.200 --> 14:19.440
does contain the Eastern Purple Lightning.

14:19.520 --> 14:22.440
But while it's powerful, it lacks a guide.

14:23.320 --> 14:26.560
It can't precisely target Jiu Ying's
spirit fragment inside his body.

14:27.160 --> 14:28.440
Your power, however,

14:29.400 --> 14:32.840
carries the force
to purify and drive out evil.

14:34.080 --> 14:34.960
Let me do it.

14:35.480 --> 14:37.120
It will consume
a vast amount of spiritual power.

14:37.880 --> 14:39.640
You only need to keep
the spirit fragment away

14:39.720 --> 14:40.600
for a short while.

14:41.360 --> 14:44.360
Otherwise, your life
will be in danger too.

15:57.640 --> 15:59.640
Only one head remains.

16:00.880 --> 16:02.000
Now it's my turn.

16:04.800 --> 16:06.120
Master Chi Wen,

16:07.880 --> 16:10.360
are you about to perform
the Scale-Descent Rite?

16:11.120 --> 16:13.480
I… I'm ready.

16:17.000 --> 16:21.080
You think a fake Dragon Deity's bracelet
can stop me?

16:21.920 --> 16:23.040
Dream on!

16:30.880 --> 16:33.960
Si Feng, since childhood, I've dreamed

16:34.480 --> 16:37.080
of becoming a double-flower hunter
and fighting by your side.

16:37.600 --> 16:39.600
Now, it's finally come true.

16:40.800 --> 16:43.200
Less talking. Focus.

16:43.280 --> 16:44.520
Or you'll be wiped out body and soul.

16:47.320 --> 16:50.600
Two mere double-flower hunters
dare stand in my way?

17:42.000 --> 17:42.920
Si Feng!

18:04.160 --> 18:05.600
Not yet, Ji Ling.

18:06.120 --> 18:09.880
After Jiu Ying's head is swallowed,
someone must wield the Guili Sword

18:09.960 --> 18:11.440
and sever my dragon body

18:11.520 --> 18:13.480
to destroy Jiu Ying completely.

18:14.160 --> 18:15.400
Really?

18:16.240 --> 18:18.760
But only a dragon can kill a dragon.

18:19.560 --> 18:20.480
Ji Ling,

18:21.640 --> 18:23.440
do you know
what I originally intended to do

18:24.040 --> 18:25.480
by putting my scale inside you?

18:27.360 --> 18:28.520
Master Chi Wen,

18:29.880 --> 18:30.960
I understand now.

18:33.000 --> 18:36.840
You meant to let your soul leave your body
after Jiu Ying was sealed.

18:37.720 --> 18:39.000
By putting a scale in me,

18:40.640 --> 18:43.640
I would become another you.

18:45.640 --> 18:49.080
Then, I was to go to the Dragon Abyss and…

18:50.680 --> 18:54.080
Then, you were to go there and kill me.

18:54.160 --> 18:55.760
So, that was the plan?

19:03.480 --> 19:05.480
But that was only the original plan.

19:06.480 --> 19:08.000
Now the plan has changed.

19:09.040 --> 19:10.080
Why?

19:12.640 --> 19:14.400
Was it…

19:16.440 --> 19:17.960
because of me?

19:22.960 --> 19:24.680
If my soul leaves my body,

19:25.200 --> 19:28.600
Jiu Ying will seize my body at once.

19:29.880 --> 19:30.720
Then what do we do?

19:31.360 --> 19:33.040
My brothers and I have created
the Tenth Dragon Son

19:33.120 --> 19:34.640
using our reverse scales.

19:34.720 --> 19:38.080
You are to guide him to the Dragon Abyss

19:38.160 --> 19:39.360
and have him kill me.

19:40.920 --> 19:42.400
However, if the last dragon

19:42.480 --> 19:44.960
in this world vanishes too,

19:45.680 --> 19:47.840
people's hope will be destroyed.

19:48.360 --> 19:51.800
As fear and hatred grow,

19:51.880 --> 19:53.080
Jiu Ying's power

19:53.680 --> 19:56.640
will surge beyond control
and become indestructible.

19:57.520 --> 19:58.720
So, Ji Ling,

20:00.440 --> 20:01.480
put on these clothes.

20:02.360 --> 20:03.720
From this moment on,

20:03.800 --> 20:06.400
you are me.

20:07.880 --> 20:09.640
Your duty is to leave hope in this world

20:11.480 --> 20:15.680
and leave behind something
for justice and kindness to rest on,

20:18.200 --> 20:21.960
even if all of it is only an illusion.

20:31.680 --> 20:32.600
I…

20:35.400 --> 20:37.680
-Master Chi Wen, I…
-From now on,

20:38.280 --> 20:39.840
you must deceive everyone,

20:41.360 --> 20:42.240
including Jiu Ying

20:42.960 --> 20:44.200
and

20:45.800 --> 20:47.000
yourself.

21:04.160 --> 21:05.880
I see.

21:09.520 --> 21:13.720
Oh, Chi Wen, what a scheme.

21:16.600 --> 21:20.480
When his mind collapses,
you can seize his body,

21:21.200 --> 21:23.960
go to the Dragon Abyss, kill Chi Wen,

21:24.880 --> 21:26.840
and free your true body.

21:28.920 --> 21:29.760
Well?

21:29.840 --> 21:33.160
That fake pretended to work with me,

21:33.240 --> 21:35.520
but all he wanted was to trick me
into destroying myself.

21:35.600 --> 21:37.920
Once you gather
all the Dragon Deity's Power,

21:38.000 --> 21:40.000
you'll naturally understand everything.

21:41.720 --> 21:44.400
So these strands of power
have been guiding me all along

21:45.880 --> 21:48.080
to fulfill my purpose
as the Tenth Dragon Son.

21:49.720 --> 21:50.800
And my purpose

21:52.960 --> 21:54.240
really is to slay the dragon.

21:56.720 --> 21:57.720
Chi Wen,

21:58.640 --> 22:01.560
you've endured the agony
of the Guili Sword all these years,

22:02.240 --> 22:03.400
planning every step,

22:05.600 --> 22:08.160
only to lead yourself to this fatal end,

22:09.200 --> 22:10.840
sacrifice yourself,

22:11.600 --> 22:13.280
and become the final seal.

22:15.440 --> 22:16.600
Too bad.

22:16.680 --> 22:20.080
I planted a spirit fragment
in your body long ago.

22:20.840 --> 22:23.360
That fake Dragon Deity
waited so long for you,

22:24.080 --> 22:26.560
and in the end,
he still couldn't tell you the truth.

22:31.600 --> 22:35.080
He must have been devastated and crushed.

22:36.000 --> 22:40.400
A grand plan a century in the making,
all ruined at the final moment.

22:43.480 --> 22:44.680
Everything

22:46.720 --> 22:48.120
that fake Dragon Deity did

22:49.200 --> 22:51.400
far surpassed
what a real one would've done.

22:52.840 --> 22:54.360
I want him to know

22:55.720 --> 22:59.000
I refuse to go on being
a Dragon Deity with no power.

23:00.960 --> 23:03.040
I want my supreme power back.

23:04.920 --> 23:07.720
I want people
to worship me for generations

23:10.720 --> 23:12.120
and revere me as their god.

23:13.080 --> 23:16.760
When you said "him",
you meant Jiu Ying, right?

23:17.920 --> 23:18.920
Ji Ling

23:22.000 --> 23:24.640
should have had a life of his own.

23:25.160 --> 23:27.680
Master Chi Wen, you've given me a name,

23:28.360 --> 23:29.520
power,

23:30.040 --> 23:33.640
and even the identity of the Dragon Deity.

23:34.240 --> 23:36.920
But I've also given you eternal shackles.

23:38.280 --> 23:39.880
You'll have to live

23:41.240 --> 23:42.240
as my shadow forever.

23:52.680 --> 23:53.760
Enough.

23:53.840 --> 23:56.600
It's time to pull out
that cursed Guili Sword.

23:56.680 --> 23:58.720
Hand your body over to me!

24:24.800 --> 24:25.720
Wu Shiguang!

24:26.640 --> 24:29.600
Wu Shiguang, wake up! Wu Shiguang!

24:34.000 --> 24:34.880
Wu Shiguang.

24:35.480 --> 24:37.400
Wu Shiguang, wake up! Wu Shiguang!

24:49.960 --> 24:50.800
You Chi, you…

24:51.920 --> 24:52.880
Wake up.

25:00.240 --> 25:01.600
Wu Shiguang?

25:06.640 --> 25:07.800
You overestimate yourself!

25:23.320 --> 25:24.840
Wu Shiguang, wake up!

25:24.920 --> 25:26.760
Wu Shiguang, wake up.

25:26.840 --> 25:28.800
Wu Shiguang, wake up! Wu Shiguang!

25:28.880 --> 25:30.600
Wake up. Wu Shiguang!

25:30.680 --> 25:31.880
Wu Shiguang…

25:33.400 --> 25:34.240
Wu Wangyan!

25:34.880 --> 25:36.160
-Wu Shiguang.
-Wangyan?

25:36.760 --> 25:37.760
Thank goodness! You're alive!

25:37.840 --> 25:39.600
-Wu Shiguang.
-Wu Shiguang!

25:39.680 --> 25:42.280
Wake up. Wake up, Wu Shiguang!

25:43.520 --> 25:45.040
Don't let Jiu Ying control you.

25:45.120 --> 25:46.240
Don't lose to him!

25:47.040 --> 25:49.560
Wu Shiguang, I'm still alive.

25:49.640 --> 25:51.040
Wu Shiguang, wake up!

25:53.640 --> 25:56.920
Wu Shiguang. Wake up, Wu Shiguang!

25:57.000 --> 25:59.280
Wu Shiguang…

25:59.360 --> 26:00.320
Wu Shiguang,

26:01.000 --> 26:01.960
I'm still alive.

26:02.040 --> 26:04.320
-Wangyan?
-Wake up!

26:04.400 --> 26:06.680
Wu Shiguang, I'm alive!

26:07.320 --> 26:08.320
It's Wangyan.

26:08.400 --> 26:10.440
I'm alive. Wake up.

26:10.520 --> 26:11.640
She's all right.

26:30.760 --> 26:31.960
How laughable.

26:32.520 --> 26:36.200
You've turned yourself
into something neither human nor ghost.

26:36.280 --> 26:39.360
Do you know why I made myself like this?

26:40.200 --> 26:41.600
For immortality?

26:42.520 --> 26:45.040
Too bad. You're going to die here today.

26:45.640 --> 26:48.240
It was so that even if my body perished,

26:48.760 --> 26:50.920
I could still destroy
evil things like you.

27:13.960 --> 27:14.920
Si Feng, no!

27:16.320 --> 27:17.520
No!

27:21.080 --> 27:22.480
My soul I devote.

27:23.680 --> 27:25.560
Long live the dragon.

27:26.680 --> 27:27.960
Si Feng!

27:37.640 --> 27:38.720
Si Feng!

27:43.680 --> 27:44.600
Si Feng…

27:46.880 --> 27:48.000
Si Feng…

28:33.440 --> 28:34.280
My brother.

29:06.960 --> 29:07.920
My brother,

29:08.440 --> 29:10.760
people worship the Dragon Deity.

29:10.840 --> 29:13.720
They carve the dragon's image
into palaces and temples

29:14.240 --> 29:16.520
and embroider it into splendid robes.

29:17.280 --> 29:19.000
They revere us.

29:19.080 --> 29:20.360
They adore us.

29:20.440 --> 29:22.400
That gives us power,

29:23.000 --> 29:24.720
but it also gives us responsibility.

29:25.680 --> 29:27.840
Even if this body of mine falls,

29:27.920 --> 29:33.400
the dragon's soul will endure forever
to protect all living beings.

29:40.440 --> 29:41.360
Jiu Ying,

29:42.920 --> 29:47.160
all you've ever brought to the world
is hatred and fear.

29:48.960 --> 29:50.640
You will never understand

29:53.880 --> 29:55.480
what it means to protect.

29:58.760 --> 30:01.640
Let scales rise,
blessing all living things.

30:05.600 --> 30:08.560
Let claws grow, sweeping away evil.

30:15.760 --> 30:19.240
Let horns rise, sheltering the world.

30:33.120 --> 30:34.160
Let eyes open,

30:36.360 --> 30:37.800
unleashing dragon's might.

30:40.920 --> 30:42.320
The dragon roars from my heart.

30:43.160 --> 30:44.600
Let scales bloom in all directions!

30:45.880 --> 30:46.720
A six-flower mark?

31:05.160 --> 31:06.960
I will fulfill the final wish my brothers

31:08.760 --> 31:09.920
left behind.

31:20.760 --> 31:23.120
Impossible! I won't die!

31:23.640 --> 31:26.840
I refuse this fate!

31:35.760 --> 31:36.600
Wu Shiguang.

31:38.120 --> 31:38.960
Wu Shiguang?

31:40.240 --> 31:42.120
Wu Shiguang, you're back.

31:42.840 --> 31:44.240
You grew horns.

31:44.320 --> 31:45.240
You've finally become a dragon.

31:46.200 --> 31:47.160
There's a flower mark too.

31:47.240 --> 31:50.080
One, two, three, four,

31:50.600 --> 31:51.440
five.

31:52.560 --> 31:54.080
You're a one-of-a-kind five-flower hunter!

31:55.800 --> 31:57.040
Count again.

31:58.920 --> 32:00.400
That's a six-flower mark.

32:29.080 --> 32:30.160
Wu Shiguang.

32:35.080 --> 32:36.080
I thought

32:39.080 --> 32:39.920
I'd lost you.

33:09.120 --> 33:10.360
You've finally come,

33:11.600 --> 33:12.520
my little brother.

33:27.440 --> 33:28.360
Shiguang,

33:30.040 --> 33:31.600
you've finally become a dragon.

33:33.160 --> 33:35.680
You now have
your own Dragon Deity's Power.

33:38.040 --> 33:39.120
Do it.

33:40.560 --> 33:42.200
Put an end to all of this.

34:39.159 --> 34:40.239
Don't be sad.

34:40.760 --> 34:42.560
After we're gone,

34:43.120 --> 34:45.800
you'll still have someone important
by your side,

34:45.880 --> 34:47.719
walking beside you.

34:48.480 --> 34:50.159
The mountains stand with you too,

34:51.120 --> 34:53.480
keeping you company.

35:00.520 --> 35:01.720
Don't be sad.

35:04.160 --> 35:05.680
I know Si Feng.

35:06.800 --> 35:08.480
She died with no regrets,

35:10.120 --> 35:11.080
because

35:13.640 --> 35:17.400
she protected
the one she wanted to protect.

35:20.160 --> 35:21.280
I know.

35:23.360 --> 35:24.760
She always said

35:26.360 --> 35:28.240
you were her only demon friend.

35:28.960 --> 35:29.800
No.

35:31.480 --> 35:33.000
The one she wanted to protect

35:33.840 --> 35:35.040
was always you.

35:39.360 --> 35:41.200
I hope Han Ba
will keep his promise and come

35:41.280 --> 35:42.880
to the Shilin Sect to face judgment.

35:43.600 --> 35:46.440
Otherwise, I'll have to drag
this deadweight here again

35:47.240 --> 35:48.320
to catch him myself.

35:51.800 --> 35:55.240
You're awfully good
to this junior brother of yours.

35:56.360 --> 35:57.240
Am I?

35:57.880 --> 35:59.560
I find him a complete nuisance.

36:02.320 --> 36:06.480
I just hope he can become
a double-flower hunter soon.

36:07.640 --> 36:11.400
That way, I won't
have to protect him all the time.

36:14.040 --> 36:16.680
But you look pretty happy doing it.

36:22.000 --> 36:23.560
I grew up an orphan.

36:24.080 --> 36:25.160
I never had any family.

36:25.680 --> 36:27.480
He's like a little brother to me.

36:28.920 --> 36:31.240
You owe me a favor, don't you?

36:35.200 --> 36:37.120
If I'm gone one day,

36:42.680 --> 36:44.840
take good care of him for me.

36:52.880 --> 36:54.560
Si Feng had no regrets.

36:55.080 --> 36:56.440
You shouldn't have any either.

36:57.080 --> 36:58.440
Your magic

36:59.480 --> 37:03.240
can protect people and save people.

37:04.360 --> 37:05.640
We all need you.

37:09.560 --> 37:10.960
I will

37:11.760 --> 37:14.400
become a great hero like her.

37:16.040 --> 37:19.360
Si Feng, I will.

37:21.520 --> 37:23.160
I promise.

37:31.920 --> 37:33.080
Where do we go next?

37:33.600 --> 37:34.680
Back to the Shilin Sect?

37:46.160 --> 37:47.440
To the Formless Moon.

37:48.120 --> 37:52.040
The last fragment of Jiu Ying's spirit
is still inside Lu Wuyi.

37:52.640 --> 37:53.960
All the spirit fragments

37:54.480 --> 37:57.040
rely on the divine power
of the Oracle Stone to survive.

37:57.680 --> 37:58.880
Only by destroying the Oracle Stone

37:59.920 --> 38:01.680
can we kill Jiu Ying for good.

38:02.360 --> 38:03.720
THE OLD DRAGON FALLS
THE NEW DRAGON RISES

38:03.800 --> 38:05.200
HEAVEN AND EARTH TREMBLE
CHAOS FILLS THE WORLD

38:05.280 --> 38:07.360
AN OLD SOUL RETURNS AGAINST TIME
A NEW MOON RESHAPES THE WORLD

38:17.240 --> 38:18.400
"The old dragon falls.

38:19.120 --> 38:20.360
The new dragon rises.

38:21.040 --> 38:21.960
Heaven and earth tremble.

38:22.480 --> 38:23.520
Chaos fills the world.

38:25.640 --> 38:27.280
An old soul returns against time.

38:27.800 --> 38:30.360
A new moon reshapes the world."

38:30.440 --> 38:32.080
Why would a new dragon

38:33.200 --> 38:34.480
bring chaos to the world?

38:35.320 --> 38:36.440
What does it mean?

38:37.920 --> 38:39.960
The new prophecy has already descended.

38:40.480 --> 38:41.840
Why isn't the Fox Queen here?

41:02.000 --> 41:04.200
Before, I fell asleep
in the main hall too.

41:05.680 --> 41:06.920
Now that I think about it,

41:09.080 --> 41:11.240
it really was you
who carried me back to my room.

41:12.000 --> 41:12.880
It was.

41:14.280 --> 41:16.920
And you kept drawing mustaches
on my statue.

41:39.840 --> 41:41.480
After everything that's happened,

41:42.800 --> 41:46.160
it feels like everything
has come full circle.

41:49.080 --> 41:51.120
As long as you're still by my side,

41:52.120 --> 41:53.600
no matter what time we return to

41:55.000 --> 41:56.120
or what we return as,

41:57.040 --> 41:58.360
I'll be content.

42:13.640 --> 42:14.960
Flowers?

42:30.000 --> 42:30.920
They smell so nice.

42:33.600 --> 42:35.200
You picked flowers for me again?

42:41.360 --> 42:42.800
Too bad you'll never

42:46.560 --> 42:48.680
be able to see
these beautiful flowers again.

42:50.840 --> 42:52.760
Even if the moon cannot be seen,

42:53.840 --> 42:57.440
those who care for it
will still keep looking up.

42:58.560 --> 43:00.600
Even if we cannot grow old together,

43:02.320 --> 43:03.840
we can still be like two distant mountains

43:04.920 --> 43:06.240
waiting for a snowfall,

43:08.680 --> 43:09.520
just like…

43:10.160 --> 43:12.400
Just like when I was haunted
by my inner demon.

43:12.480 --> 43:16.800
Even when I couldn't see you,
you were still by my side,

43:17.560 --> 43:18.800
keeping me company

43:20.680 --> 43:21.640
and saving me.
